org.apache.felix.ipojo.dependency.interceptors

Class DefaultServiceRankingInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.dependency.interceptors.DefaultDependencyInterceptor
      • org.apache.felix.ipojo.dependency.interceptors.DefaultServiceRankingInterceptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DependencyInterceptor, ServiceRankingInterceptor

    public class DefaultServiceRankingInterceptor
extends DefaultDependencyInterceptor
implements ServiceRankingInterceptor
    Default implementation of the default service ranking interceptor. This implementation does not sort the given set, so returns it as it is. It also provides an `invalidateSelectedServices` method notifying all managed dependencies of a change in the selection service set. onDeparture, onArrival and onModified methods delegates to the getServiceReferences method.

      • invalidateSelectedServices

        public void invalidateSelectedServices()
        Notifies the managed dependencies of a change in the set of services selected by this interceptor. The dependency will call the getServiceReferences method to recompute the set of selected services.
